  "instructions": [
    "season the steak with black pepper and set aside.",
    "heat the olive oil in the iron teppan pan over medium-high heat.",
    "sous-vide the steak to 130f for 1-2 hours.",
    "remove the steak from the sous-vide machine and let rest.",
    "in a small bowl, whisk together chilli bean paste, grapefruit juice, soy sauce, and sugar.",
    "add the green onions and garlic to the bowl and mix well.",
    "brush the glaze all over the steak.",
    "grill the steak on the iron teppan pan for 2-3 minutes per side, or until cooked to desired level of doneness.",
    "let the steak rest for 5 minutes before slicing.",
    "serve the steak with the glaze spooned over the top, and a dollop of sour cream if desired.",
    "serve immediately and enjoy!",
    " Garnish with additional green onions if desired."
  ],
